snippet.title: Magic Mike XXL Movie Review / The Kevin ShimShow
snippet.description:
On the third episode of The Kevin ShimShow, Kevin reviews the 2015 film, Magic Mike XXL starring Channing Tatum, Amber Heard, Andie McDowell, Elizabeth Banks, Michael Strahan, and Jada Pinkett Smith. Also featured on this episode, a Kevin ShimShow News Story Joke of the week about Bill Cosby.

Subscribe to my channel please! Be kind and share with your friends/family. I apologize for my lack of clothes in this episode. 

https://www.kevinshimko.com
